snippet.title: Night chat about Amber Heard abuse and how she used everybody's for her gain.And "cut me" audio
snippet.description: On this live I sat down and listened to the heart breaking audio of Johnny and Amber on the cutting incident in which he begs her to cut him ,I was trying to put two and two together with the text messages with pictures of the knives that Amber and minions were sending to each other and if anybody was doing this on purpose or just happens to be coincidental . Is very sad to listen to him in so much emotional pain but even if he is self harming or engaged in any behavior that is self destructive DOES NOT make him a wife beater ,this shows you how much helped he needed and instead he got recorded and blamed instead . Why she is recording this why in this moment ? More on Amber narc tactis and abuse of her sister ,ex assistant ,her mother and who know who else. Kate James her assistant from 2013 to 2017 told her in confidence her abuse and rape history that it happened to her 26 years a go and Amber use this on her own narrative ,this is how she got attention and sympathy using SOMEBODY else' rape hear breaking history . This woman should be hold accountable or at least cross examine better in 2022, Lets hope. #justiceforjohnny #ibelievejohnnydepp   #amberheardabuse #johnnyaudiocutting #amberheardjohnnydeppcase #cuttingdeppaudio #justicefordepp #mendomesticviolence #abusetomen
